Package: bio3d.ggplot
Type: Package
Title: Plot Matrix Data From The bio3d Package With ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Barry Grant
Maintainer: Barry Grant <barryus@gmail.com>
Description: Utility functions for plotting bio3d matrix data including
    distance matrices, contact maps, correlation plots (DCCMs), pca and nma
    results using ggplot2 rather than the base and grid graphics functions
    included in the bio3d package itself.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    bio3d,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
